title: Dark Whooshes - Sound Effects
description: Alot of dark whooshes for your game!
longDescription:
Hi Dev!


In this package you will have access to 100 dark whoosh files to be used in the most diverse situations, from cinematics to magic.


Check the preview

Check the documentation


Variety

As mentioned above, the sounds are very versatile and it is possible to imagine them being used in very diverse situations, such as a warlock's magic, or in a horror cinematic before a jumpscare, even a large vehicle passing by the character, and with some pitch changes you can create hundreds of other useful variations for your game!


Originality

All the sounds were recorded in very creative ways, sheets, rugs and cloths swaying, wind inside different shapes, cylinders, pipes, bottles, pots. Sounds edited on synthesizers to sound different from reality, and even several mixes of all of this to guarantee unique sounds for you!


Quality and support

All files were recorded using professional equipment and edited in post-production with specific software, ensuring the quality of the sound effects files. You also have access to my personal email to send any message if you need any support with the archives.


Helping each other

By investing in this package you get all of this and still inspire me to continue creating for the community
